- **Sea North Kayaking**  
  - Out on the Churchill River, surrounded by hundreds of playful belugas.  
  - They are drawn to sound, so we sang show tunes—*"Hey, Big Spender"* was a hit!  
  - We were part of a group of over 40 kayakers; orientation took a while, but we got the full two hours in the water.

