- **Car rental for bear spotting and general shenanigans**  
  - Limited public routes; we could not leave the vehicle.  
  - Spotted one bear on a spit and another galloping across the way!
  - We got to enjoy a beautiful sunset we would otherwise have missed.
  - Don't ask about the flat tire. Regan is starting to collect them in various countries through no fault of her own.

